  "prompt": "What is the best time to visit Kanniyakumari?",
  "response": "The best time to visit Kanniyakumari, located at the southern tip of India, is typically during the winter months from October to March. During this period, the weather is more pleasant and cooler compared to the hot and humid conditions prevalent during the rest of the year. This season offers ideal temperatures for sightseeing and exploring the area\u2019s attractions, such as the Vivekananda Rock Memorial, Thiruvalluvar Statue, and the pristine beaches. Additionally, visiting during the winter allows you to experience clearer skies and enjoy the famous sunrise and sunset views that Kanniyakumari is known for.",
